left_text: Propodeum with postspiracular fovea; T6 of male without lateral lobe; S4 of male with median comb, S5 with comb laterally (nearctic, Mesoamerica)
right_text: Propodeum without postspiracular fovea or with fovea only about the size of the spiracle; T6 of male with lateral lobe; sterna of male without combs (Mesoamerica)
